For my project I implemented 2 bots, in the form of 2 seperate spy bots, and 2 separate resistance bots.


Separate bots:
	expertSpyBot21503324.java	- simple expert spy bot
	expertResistanceBot21503324.java	- simple expert resistance bot
	bayBot2103324.java		- resistance bot using Bayesian updates
	smartSpy21503324.java		- spy bot using Monte Carlo Tree

Combined bots:
	firstBot21503324.java	- Combines on expertSpyBot and bayBot from above, the most successful
	secondBot21503324.java	- Combines on expertResistanceBot and smartSpy from above, the least successful

Misc:
	superGame21503324.java  - an edited version of Game.java needed for the Monte Carlo Tree
	GeneticAlgorithm21503324.java 	- a genetic algorithm used to optimise bayBot
	MonteCarloTree21503324.java	- implementation behind smartSpy
	bayStats21503324.java		- implementation behind bayBot

Demonstration:
	testGame21503324.java	- contains a few demonstration/testing functions
